Requirements

Software Requirements

Modern web browser such as Chrome, Firefox, Edge, or Safari

Optional: Git and GitHub account for uploading the project

Hardware Requirements

Any desktop, laptop, tablet, or mobile device with internet access

Responsive design works on small and large screens

Programming / Development Requirements

HTML for the structure of the game

CSS for styling, responsive design, and animations

JavaScript for game logic, car movement, LCM calculation, and interactivity
